data.description: A rare 2,394 sqft home sitting on a 1-acre corner lot with incredible views of hills and mountains from every window. Back deck recently updated and refinished.  Spacious ranch-style home featuring 4 bedrooms 3 baths. Open floor plan with a great room featuring a wood-burning fireplace and a bonus room featuring a wood stove. Wonderful split floor plan with a private primary suite featuring a soaking tub and walk-in shower. Fully fenced property with a separate fenced area in the back for any pets. Furnace is only a year old and has AC.
